annotation.text: User Administration flow , which allows Admin to Add a new user , Update User Profile with contact info,Role etc.. and also to delete the particular user.
Add User Flow - 1.Creates the user with the details provided by Admin 2.Adds the user to the respective group in Appian based on Role provided. 3.Details persisted to DB.
Edit Users Flow -Updates the user details which are entered. 1. Group Changes - User Deleted from old Group and Added to new Group. 2.Final Details persisted in DB.
Delete User Flow - 1. Deactivates the user from Appian System. 2. Deletes the selected users from DB.
